colSd <- function (x, na.rm=FALSE) apply(X=x, MARGIN=2, FUN=sd, na.rm=na.rm)

CI <- function(x, level = 0.95) {
  alpha <- 1 - level
  ci <- mean(x) + c(-1, 1) * qnorm(1 - (alpha / 2)) * sqrt(var(x) / length(x))
  return(ci)
}
